headline.print_headline: Bale Stunner Claims Cup Win for Real Over Barca
headline.main: Bale Stunner Claims Cup Win for Real Over Barca

lead_paragraph: Gareth Bale raced away to score a stunning late winner as Real Madrid made light of the absence of top scorer Cristiano Ronaldo to beat arch-rivals Barcelona 2-1 to win a riveting King's Cup final on Wednesday.
